ygData.messageBody:
In that area Dungeon-wise there are still some things in BlackBurrow by
Qeynos you can take, and the same with Paw...I'll bet you could just hang
out in the first room or 2, and just take the regular Gnolls that spawn
there. I'm level 17 and I'm just hanging out there gettin revenge for the
countless Gnoll related death. I'm on Povar as well, if you do go there, say
hi to Rolande if I'm still there.
-----Original Message-----
From: Shining Path <shining_path@...>

>Greetings all,
>I have enjoyed this list tremendously. My partner and I are both level 10

>would like to travel to new lands, can anyone suggest some good areas where
>we can hang our shingle up and not spend too much time finding our corpses?
>
>Fidel 10th Chord
>Povar
